OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FGenerally a bit cloudier on Saturday,
OL,7,Fbut mostly dry with some sunny spells.
OL,8,FSunshine returning more widely for
OL,9,FSunday and Monday. Temperatures
OL,10,Fgenerally remaining above average, and
OL,11,Ffeeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
